sub_title: Learning Support Assistant for students with additional educational needs
summary: Learning Support Assistant aiding students with additional educational needs. M. Phil. in English Language Teaching from Trinity College Dublin. Undergraduate from Dalhousie University with BA double major in Environment, Society & Sustainability Studies (ESS) and French language. My diverse background in various fields has introduced me to constructive approaches toward teaching and support. First-hand international experience the the US, Canada, France, Ireland and now permanently the Netherlands has given me the beneficial flexibility to live and work multilingually and multiculturally.
